{"tid":2419394,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"8人黃大仙非法集結表證不成立 律政司決定提出上訴","createTime":"2021-02-23T09:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T18:33:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"674e3cfad9618de9ab579c7193bf6c1ddfb470f1","tid":2419394,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5260\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F5260&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv3%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=24980854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/5260</a><br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】前年國慶多區爆發衝突，9人被控於黃大仙區參與非法集結，其中8名男女早前獲裁判官黃士翔裁定非法集結罪全部表證不成立，當庭獲釋。本報得悉，律政司今已決定就8人的表證不成立提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n餘下一名30歲女護士則表證成立。裁判官於本月19日於西九龍裁判法院裁定女護士罪名不成立，指出當日黃大仙不同地方也有人集結堵路，控方無足夠證據證明她於控罪書上的街道非法集結。（全文）<br />\n<br />\n#20210223新聞 #1001黃大仙"},{"pid":"b9a33dae85764cb10d07c19bd66eee1bfcad6389","tid":2419394,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db039b4f9c88eda3d930894af19496316885b44d","tid":2419394,"uid":270307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4133c23f2c32df04c65dac267b44adf109b60ea","tid":2419394,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d